org.apache.flink.api.java.typeutils

类 ValueTypeInfo<T extends Value>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.common.typeinfo.TypeInformation<T>
      • org.apache.flink.api.java.typeutils.ValueTypeInfo<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - The type of the class represented by this type information.
    所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable, AtomicType<T>

    @Public
public class ValueTypeInfo<T extends Value>
extends TypeInformation<T>
implements AtomicType<T>
    Type information for data types that extend the Value interface. The value interface allows types to define their custom serialization and deserialization routines.
    另请参阅:
